<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Grazzt</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-11-06 14:27:38</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have recently acquired this staff on the Bertox server from a friendly level 60 druid.  I was able to get this staff at an UNBELIEVABLE price, largely because this druid wanted to get his buddy a Bonecaster Robe, which was part of what I traded.  Anyway, I have had (no kidding) at least 100 /t in first 3 days since acquiring this staff asking its stats, its price, etc.  I know of only 3 other people on the server that own this cool looking stick.  The price you see listed is a joke...in the 3 days I've owned this staff, I've been offered  1) 45,000pp   2) 2 manastones  3) Bonecaster Robes, Heirophant Cloak, and Efreeti Boots     I've been offered these deals and I've not once even /auctioned that I own it - people see it and send me /t!  Anyway, just wanted to mention that I own one, and I'm kinda pumped about it.  Peace.</font></td></tr></table>
